message: Fayetteville Police Department’s Human Trafficking Unit and Sheriff Ennis W. Wright: Cumberland County NC's Human Trafficking Unit along with other law enforcement agencies and non- profits in their region are dedicated to and helping victims of human trafficking. Great job on disrupting illicit massage businesses in NC!
